In a large skillet, melt butter over medium heat. Add leeks; saute, stirring occasionally, for 10 minutes. Stir in apples, celery and mushrooms; saute, stirring occasionally, for 8 minutes. Transfer the mixture to a large bowl. Stir in breadcrumbs, Lindsay Olives, broth, walnuts, parsley, sage and thyme; mix well. Season with salt and pepper. Stuffing can be served immediately or cooled and stuffed into a turkey ready to be roasted.